from now on only PositionManager is allowed to remove itself as a manager by calling Pool.revokeLPsManager function).
Following deposit related actions (that could affect LP balance at index) are disallowed for LP owner as long as the manager is set to PositionManager:
approve another position manager by calling Pool.approveLPsManager for same index
moveQuoteToken at index
removeQuoteToken at index
kickWithDeposit at index
removeCollateral at index
(NFT) mergeOrRemoveCollateral using index
